summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department; authorizing an easement agreement with King County, Washington, for the extension of S.E. 83rd Place in the plat of Olympus, Division 1, across the City's East Side Supply Line right of way in the northeast quarter of Section 33, Township 24 North, Range 5 East, W.M., in King County, Washington, and accepting as consideration therefor a quit claim deed to certain real property situated in said Section 33.
